In the five days since Roger Stone was hit with a comprehensive gag order for threatening a federal judge, he’s been behaving surprisingly well in public.
Stone seems to think he’s found a clever way around this on Instagram.
Okay, this by itself was probably allowable under the terms of his gag order.
Roger Stone seems intent on inching further and further up against the line.
Stone may think he’s being clever here, but the judge is going to drop the hammer on him if he keeps it up – and knowing him, he’ll definitely keep it up.